  "texts": [
    "The accuracy decreases when the aggregate request rate increases.",
    "Here, the aggregate request rate can increase when the number of clients or their frame rate increases.",
    "In this case, the scheduler has to lower the DNNs sizes to support the higher request rates.",
    "However, with larger SLOs, the scheduler can select larger DNNs when possible.",
    "Consequently, the accuracy at 150ms SLO for all settings is higher than that at 100ms or 75ms SLOs."
  ],
